sources.title: The Swiss Conspiracy (1976 Thriller) with David Janssen | Dirty Money, Dirty Secrets... 4K
sources.description:
You can hide anything in a Swiss bank except... murder!
David Christopher, an ex–U.S. Justice Department operative, scrambles to shield a Zurich bank’s blackmailed clients, but Johann Hurtil’s lethal ledger demands a bloodier balance. Teaming with Denise Abbott and rogue agent Robert Hayes, the trio dodges double-crosses in a high-stakes race across Zurich, where every transaction could be their last deposit—unless they withdraw the truth in a finale wired to blow!

Director: Jack Arnold
Writers: Norman Klenman, Horward Merrill, Philip Saltzman

Main cast:
David Janssen – David Christopher
Senta Berger – Denise Abbott
John Ireland – Dwight McGowan
John Saxon – Robert Hayes
Ray Milland – Johann Hurtil
Elke Sommer – Rita Jensen
Anton Diffring – Franz Benninger
Arthur Brauss – Andre Kosta
Inigo Gallo – Captain Frey
Curt Lowens – Korsak

Genres: Action, Crime, Drama, Thriller
Release Date: March 1, 1976
Filming Location: Zurich, Switzerland
